If you run the below scritpt you will get “Code is Blasted”

Explain Why the Code is blasted and how to diffuse it and get “Diffused":


1. Here two strings are being compared and hence 2 is compared with 1 and as 2>1, value of a is true and hence code is blasted.
   The value of a should be false to get Diffused.
    var a = "2" < "12";
    //Don't touch below this
    if (a) {
      console.log("Code is Blasted")
    }
    else
    {
      console.log("Diffused") 
    }
    
    
 How to get Success in following code?:
 
